1. OSI 7 Layer

Application → Layanan langsung ke user (HTTP, FTP, DNS, SMTP, dll).

Presentation → Format data, enkripsi, kompresi.

Session → Mengatur komunikasi antar aplikasi.

Transport → Pengiriman end-to-end (TCP, UDP).

Network → Routing data (IP).

Data Link → Frame, MAC address, ARP/RARP.

Physical → Media fisik (kabel, fiber optic, wireless).

2. TCP/IP Model (lebih sederhana & modular)

Application Layer → HTTP, FTP, DNS, SMTP, SSH, Telnet.

Transport Layer → TCP, UDP.

Internet Layer → IP.

Network Access Layer → ARP, RARP, Ethernet, WiFi.

3. Konsep Data Transmission

Encapsulation & Decapsulation → Data dibungkus sesuai layer.

Bentuk data:

Bit stream (Physical)

Frame (Data Link)

Packet (Network)

Segment/Datagram (Transport)

Data (Application)

4. Media Komunikasi

Cable (UTP/STP)

Fiber Optic (FO)

Radio Frequency (RF / Wireless)
